       "model": "One cold morning last November, my friend Dan and I set out before dawn to catch the early train into the city. We had planned the trip for a week, and Dan's father had promised to drive us to the station. But the car would not start, and by the time we ran the last half mile, the platform was empty. The red lights of the train were already shrinking down the track. We sat on the bench and laughed at ourselves, then walked home to wait for the next one.",
