       "q": "Theme VI. Write a short theme, using one of the subjects below. You need not tell something which actually happened, but it should be so told that your readers will think it might have happened. 1. A trip in a sailboat. 2. The travels of a penny. 3. How I was lost. 4. A cat's account of a mouse hunt. 5. The mouse's account of the same hunt. 6. My experience with a burglar. 7. The burglar's story.",
