       "id": "comp-2-4-e5",
       "type": "compose",
       "q": "Theme IX. Write a story that will account for the condition shown in a picture you have chosen. (Correct with reference to clearness and meaning. Do you need to change the sentence length either for the sake of clearness or for the sake of variety? Cross out unnecessary ands. Underscore got and then each time you have used them. Can the reader follow the thread of your story to its chief point?)",
