       "type": "compose",
       "q": "Theme XIV. Write a story suggested by one of the following subjects: a modern fable; the willow whistle; the delayed picnic; a ride on a raft; a railway experience. (Have you needed to use figures? If so, have you used them in accordance with the suggestions on page 55?)",
