       "type": "compose",
       "q": "Theme XXII. Write a paragraph by giving details for one of the following topic statements: 'The sounds heard in the forest at night are somewhat alarming to one who is not used to the language of the woods'; 'There were many interesting things on the farm where I spent my summer vacation.' (Do the details bear upon the main idea?)",
