       "type": "compose",
       "q": "Theme XCII. Develop one of the following topic statements into an expository paragraph by use of examples: 1. Weather depends to a great extent upon winds. 2. Progress in civilization has been materially aided by the use of nails. 3. Habit is formed by the repetition of the same act. 4. Men become criminals by a gradual process. 5. Men's lives are affected by small things. 6. Defeat often proves to be real success.",
